{
  "text": "Some scholars and practitioners have gone even further by designing and conducting ongoing mindfulness training in the classroom across curriculum to support an attentive, present centered, and non-reactive mental mode [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] as well as by development and standardization of mindfulness qualities scale for college students [CITATION_3] .",
